      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. All body panels are original with perfect factory gaps, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and show no signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It boasts a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather use. Included with the sale are all original keys, the owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that is, for all intents and purposes, indistinguishable from new.",
